# Copy this file to .dev.vars and fill in values
# Used by wrangler dev for local development

# No required secrets for the API worker currently
# Auth is validated against the D1 auth_sessions table
#
# Email sending (password reset, etc.) uses the SEND_EMAIL binding
# configured in wrangler.jsonc — no env var needed for local dev.
# The binding sends from noreply@corlify.com.
